/**
 * One-time migration: retroactively classify existing posts and papers into
 * research topics using Claude-generated classifications.
 *
 * - Skips announcements entirely.
 * - Skips posts/papers that already have topics.
 * - Uses updateOne() to avoid triggering pre-save hooks or ES sync,
 *   so the running app is not affected.
 *
 * Usage: node scripts/migrate-topics-gemini.js
 */

